Package big.process1D.spline

Class Summary
Bspline This class deals with polynomial B-splines.
SplineData This class encapsulates operations on one-dimensional spline data.
 

Enum Summary
SplineBasis This enumerated type describes the type of basis used to build a continuously-defined representation of the data given by a discrete set of values.
